      public void processBlock(int x, int y, int z, WorldRegion region)
      Description copied from class: KeystoneFilter
      Ran for every block the filter is modifying after KeystoneFilter.processRegion(WorldRegion). Use this for modifications that can be done on a per-block basis. Be sure that this code is self-contained, as this will be ran on multiple threads for improved performance, and as such is subject to race conditions
